message.body: Lindsey said you were trying to do something this weekend, but I am going down to Asheville to look at this property
I can come get my stuff tomorrow or Thursday
Tomorrow later in the day or Thursday whenever.
Are you going to sell your house to buy that place?
I don't know but I want to at least go see it and talk to the guy to see if we can work something out with his moving schedule and mine. There are a few options but most likely I need to sell
Daaamn. That is nuts. Will you be around next weekend?
I have no clue but I don't currently have any plans for the weekend of the 23rd
Where you at? I need the van soon.
Oh. I'll drive it back over in a minute
